 Client Relationship Executive 
 Location: Las Vegas, NV
Electrum Partners is seeking a driven candidate to pursue, grow, and sustain strategic executive relationships as we continue to lead the industry in developing markets, and key players, in legal cannabis-related businesses in North America.
Candidates should have a strong entrepreneurial spirit, relevant industry experience (Business Consulting or Technology Sales, Financial Services/Investment Banking/Capital Formation), strong relationship management skills and a proven track record in selling professional services. To emphasize, we are seeking candidates who have the ability to maintain a high level of productivity and manage multiple competing priorities. Prospective candidates must be able to work effectively under the pressure of time constraints in a fast-paced, complex, collaborative, and team-oriented environment.

	The Client Relationship Executive (CRE) is responsible for building and maintaining the relationship between our firm and current and future clients. You will market EP's services and capabilities to the client, and assist with identifying and planning additional opportunities for the firm to pursue.  The candidate will understand how to develop an integrated marketing plan that targets specific verticals within the industry based on corporate objectives.  The candidate will understand the professional service delivery process and have a history of delivering successful engagements during the majority of their career.
 
 Apply for this Job 
  

  
  
 Graphic Artist 
 Location: New York, NY
Seeking experienced creative director/graphics designer for an exciting growth opportunity in the legal cannabis industry.  We are ushering in a new era at Electrum Partners, based on a philosophy of compassion, social justice and innovation.  Our company is fueled with passion about helping others succeed and navigate within the wide spectrum of the cannabis business ecosystem.  We are Electrum Partners and we lead with best practices.
You are that rare creative genius who exists in the space where artistry meets execution and blowing minds does not mean blowing deadlines. We do cutting edge work that shapes and reshapes the reality of an exciting industry that is changing everything. You give those projects form and color, you make them real and a little unreal.  We know cannabis, you know every design medium there is. We never stop moving. You are one step ahead. Together we define what is next.  
This unique opportunity is for ambitious individuals who are looking to be part of a new movement in the legal cannabis industry. Candidates should be talented designers looking to grow, manage, and design many different types of innovative and creative material. Electrum Partners is a motivated and innovative firm, and expects its employees to work in a similar fashion.
 
