Electrum Partners, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 11:59 AM ET
Professional Services

Company Overview of Electrum Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Electrum Partners, LLC provides advisory and consulting services specializing in the legal cannabis industry in the United States. Its business services include business creation, business incubation, application package development, strategic and tactical guidance, assistance with capital formation, business development and accretive relationships, support navigating political landscapes and regulatory processes, and industry-specific expertise. The company also publishes the Electrum Report, available at electrumreport.com, a curated service that includes summaries and links to industry-relevant news. Additionally, it offers strategic management consulting services to public and private co...
Electrum Partners, LLC provides advisory and consulting services specializing in the legal cannabis industry in the United States. Its business services include business creation, business incubation, application package development, strategic and tactical guidance, assistance with capital formation, business development and accretive relationships, support navigating political landscapes and regulatory processes, and industry-specific expertise. The company also publishes the Electrum Report, available at electrumreport.com, a curated service that includes summaries and links to industry-relevant news. Additionally, it offers strategic management consulting services to public and private companies that are looking to maximize shareholder value and shareholder liquidity, as well as companies that are making the private-to-public transition. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
