Company Description


Electrum Partners is a boutique consulting firm specializing in the nascent Medical Marijuana industry in the United States. Founded by Leslie Bocskor, a seasoned investment banker experienced in disruptive markets and technologies, the firm provides business services, strategic guidance and introductions, and industry-specific expertise to those applying for licensure or currently operating within the United States legal Cannabis industry.

Additionally, Electrum Partners offers strategic management consulting to public and private companies that are looking to maximize shareholder value and shareholder liquidity, as well as companies that are making the private-to-public transition.




